<div class="relative text-[3vw] p-[6vw] sm:text-[2vw] md:text-[1.5vw] lg:text-[1.2vw] font-sans">
    <p class="mb-5 sm:my-3">DGT will be the Project Sponsor to develop the Integrated Domestic Gas to Power Project in Myanmar which received an exclusive right to and signed the Notice to Proceed with Ministry of Electricity and Energy (MOEE) on 30 December 2020.</p>
    <p>The project will promote the utilization of domestic gas supplied from the producing and exploration projects in the Gulf of Mataban starting from Zawtika and Myanmar M3 projects.</p>
